### GET /news (default category = tech)
GET http://localhost:8080/news

### GET /news?category=tech
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=tech

### GET /news?category=tech&topics=3
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=tech&topics=3

### GET /news?category=economy
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=economy

### GET /news?category=science
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=science

### GET /news?category=ai
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=ai

### GET /news?category=security
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=security

### GET /news?category=startups
GET http://localhost:8080/news?category=startups